title: UFOs and the FBI - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/16/22
itunes:title: UFOs and the FBI - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/16/22
description:
George Noory and retired FBI agent John DeSouza explore his career investigating paranormal cases in the bureau, from violent bank robberies to suspected UFO sightings by pilots, and whether the government is reverse engineering UFO technology.
